A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating the H. G. Yeomans III Family Trust, the 2024 Georgia Tree Farmer of the
2 Year; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, at the Georgia Forestry Association's Annual Conference & Forestry Expo in
4 Savannah, the Georgia Tree Farm Program named the H. G. Yeomans III Family Trust as the
5 2024 Georgia Tree Farmer of the Year in recognition of their outstanding forest management
6 and dedication to sustainable land stewardship; and
7 WHEREAS, presented through the American Tree Farm System, this prestigious award
8 honors private landowners who demonstrate forestry practices that support local wildlife,
9 wood production, water conservation, and recreational opportunities; and
10 WHEREAS, established in the 1700s, the Yeomans family farm has grown from its original
11 275 acres to encompass 2,300 acres of beautifully kept land; and
12 WHEREAS, their logging business, Yeomans Wood and Timber, is widely recognized for
13 its commitment to forest stewardship, employing sustainable forestry management practices
14 such as prescribed fire, native longleaf pine restoration, and wildlife habitat preservation; and
