15 WHEREAS, they have additionally integrated soil and water-friendly road construction,
16 designed custom deer stands to accommodate physically disabled outdoor enthusiasts, and
17 repurposed reclaimed wood and bricks from old farm structures for educational events and
18 family gatherings; and
19 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this exemplary family be appropriately
20 honored during this special time.
21 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
22 the members of this body congratulate the H. G. Yeomans III Family Trust upon their
23 recognition as the 2024 Georgia Tree Farmer of the Year as well as extend best wishes for
24 continued success.
25 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
26 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
27 H. G. Yeomans III Family Trust.
